  "text": "and E(r) = \u03b5/10, r = 0 min{\u03b2(r), \u03b5/10}, r \u2265 1 [CITATION_1] Set m = 10/\u03b5 and S(\u03b5) = S 2.7 (10/\u03b5, E), hence S(\u03b5) is a function of \u03b5 and P only. We also set",
  "correct_citation": {
